description: Lists the resources that are not currently supported in Resilience Hub. An unsupported resource is a resource that exists in the object that was used to create an app, but is not supported by Resilience Hub.

parameters.name: appArn
parameters.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Resilience Hub application. The format for this ARN is: arn: partition:resiliencehub: region: account:app/ app-id. For more information about ARNs, see Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) in the Amazon Web Services General Reference guide.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: Token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: resolutionId
nested_items.description: The identifier for a specific resolution.

nested_items.name: unsupportedResources
nested_items.description: The unsupported resources for the application.

nested_items.name: logicalResourceId
nested_items.description: Logical resource identifier for the unsupported resource.

nested_items.name: eksSourceName
nested_items.description: Name of the Amazon Elastic Kubernetes Service cluster and namespace this resource belongs to.

nested_items.name: identifier
nested_items.description: Identifier of the resource.

nested_items.name: logicalStackName
nested_items.description: The name of the CloudFormation stack this resource belongs to.

nested_items.name: resourceGroupName
nested_items.description: The name of the resource group that this resource belongs to.

nested_items.name: terraformSourceName
nested_items.description: The name of the Terraform S3 state file this resource belongs to.

nested_items.name: physicalResourceId
nested_items.description: Physical resource identifier for the unsupported resource.

nested_items.name: awsAccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account that owns the physical resource.

nested_items.name: awsRegion
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services Region that the physical resource is located in.

nested_items.name: identifier
nested_items.description: Identifier of the physical resource.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: Specifies the type of physical resource identifier.
AWS::ECS::Service.
AWS::EFS::FileSystem.
AWS::ElasticLoadBalancingV2::LoadBalancer.
AWS::Lambda::Function.
AWS::SNS::Topic.

nested_items.name: resourceType
nested_items.description: The type of resource.

nested_items.name: unsupportedResourceStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the unsupported resource.
